msgstr "[dosya bütünlüğü](https://gitlab.com/fdroid/fdroidclient/blob/v0.101-alpha2/app/src/main/java/org/fdroid/fdroid/installer/ApkCache.java#L57) [imzalı üst veri](https://gitlab.com/fdroid/fdroidclient/blob/v0.101-alpha2/app/src/main/java/org/fdroid/fdroid/RepoUpdater.java#L212) tarafından korunmaktadır"

#. type: Bullet: '-   '
#: _docs/Security_Model.md
msgid "As of [_index-v2_](https://gitlab.com/fdroid/fdroidserver/-/merge_requests/1092), files from the repo are verified based on SHA-256, including icons, screenshots, etc."
